==Finnish==
===Noun===

'''hitto''' (plural ''hitot'')

''(mild expletive)'' Hell, fuck, heck, or shit. Somewhat comparable to Geezers!

===Usage notes===

''Hitto'' is technically a noun but it can't be an object, like [[helvetti]] or [[vittu]]. Therefore, you can say ''mene helvettiin'' or ''painu vittuun'' to tell someone to get lost, but you can't say ''mene hittoon''.

